title: Holy Night (feat. Erika Sirola)
lyrics:
O holy night, the stars are brightly shining
It is the night of the dear Savior's birth
O holy night, the fire is slowly dying
And here we lay on the snow covered earth
Hear the angels sing from up high

Oh night divine, please be mine



Oh night when Christ was born

Oh

Oh night when Christ was born



O holy night, the moonlight guides His own words

Along the road to the manger He lays

O holy night, the silence only wanders

He walks alone down the snow covered lanes



Hear the angels sing from up high

Oh night divine, please be mine

Hear the angels sing from up high

Hear their voices ring from the height

Oh night divine, please be mine



Oh night when Christ was born

Oh

Oh night when Christ was born



Hear the angels sing from up high

Oh night divine, please be mine

Hear their voices ring from the height

Oh night divine, please be mine
